title: Las Lagartijas
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Restaurant and store (aka Gourmet Garage) in a serene area. In-house condiments and menu includes some veg friendly hot sandwiches served using whole wheat or sourdough bread, plus Mexican food, stir fries, a varied range of house-made pickles, jam, and salsa.
streetAddress: dirt road going to El Bambu
